# strategies/

Drop `.qkt` files in this directory. They're mounted into the running daemon at
`/strategies` (read-only).

To deploy one:

```bash
make deploy STRAT=ema_cross
```

That runs `qkt deploy /strategies/ema_cross.qkt --as ema_cross` inside the
container. The daemon registers it and starts evaluating rules on the next tick.

To stop one:

```bash
make stop STRAT=ema_cross
```

